{"tid":1174521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"88歲男子疑因病厭世攀窗墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-28T02:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T02:49:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4bb1a761067dd6595dbc53a6adca3c28c10074","tid":1174521,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"葵涌安蔭邨康蔭樓，凌晨4時許，一名88歲姓吳男子，從大廈高處墮下，倒卧簷篷昏迷不醒，家人發現報警。消防員到場協助，用升降台將男子救下，由救護員送院搶救，惜傷重終告不治。警員進行調查，懷疑死者因病厭世，從單位窗口攀出墮樓輕生，案件初步並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=a5b81827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190528/59648814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F59648814&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=d0d5dde3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F59648814&h=9706a0f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190528/59648814</a>"},{"pid":"4f1fbde2e2b3eec4f90c0b281ced79ec0a54d5c8","tid":1174521,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:05:05.000Z","msg":"好彩無壓到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ceee358c88a53b6956dbcd314fbf37cd20770a","tid":1174521,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42